name: Stats.NormalDistribution
comment:
A library for stats calculations.

@docs zScore, cdf, cdfZ

values.name: cdf
values.comment:
cdf value mean std =
        let
            z_ =
                zScore value mean std
        in
        cdfZ z_

values.name: cdfZ
values.comment:
Returns the probability given the normal distribution Z value.

    cdfZ 2.4 -- "Just 0.9918"
    cdfZ 2.44444444444 -- "Just 0.9927"
    cdfZ -2.4 -- "Just 0.0082"
